#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using <span class=\"application\">GNOME Disks</span>"
msgstr "Utilitzant <span class=\"application\">Discs de GNOME</span>"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"caution\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"caution\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<strong>You might overwrite any hard disk on the computer.</strong> If at some\n"
"point you are not sure about which device to choose, stop proceeding.\n"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Podeu sobreescriure qualsevol disc dur de l'ordinador.</strong> Si "
"no esteu\n"
"segur de quin dispositiu triar, millor no continueu.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Make sure that the USB stick that you want to reset is unplugged."
msgstr ""
"Assegureu-vos que el llapis USB que voleu restablir estigui desconnectat."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"1. Choose\n"
"   <span class=\"menuchoice\">\n"
"     <span class=\"guimenu\">Applications</span>&nbsp;▸\n"
"     <span class=\"guisubmenu\">Utilities</span>&nbsp;▸\n"
"     <span class=\"guimenuitem\">Disks</span>\n"
"   </span>\n"
"   to start <span class=\"application\">GNOME Disks</span>.\n"
msgstr ""
"1. Trieu\n"
"    <span class=\"menuchoice\">\n"
"      <span class=\"guimenu\">Aplicacions</span>&nbsp;▸\n"
"      <span class=\"guisubmenu\">Utilitats</span>&nbsp;▸\n"
"      <span class=\"guimenuitem\">Discs</span>\n"
"    </span>\n"
"    per iniciar <span class=\"application\">Discs de GNOME</span>.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   A list of all the storage devices on the computer appears in the left pane\n"
"   of the window.\n"
msgstr ""
"   Al panell esquerre de la finestra apareix una llista de tots els "
"dispositius\n"
"   d'emmagatzematge de l'ordinador.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Plug in the USB stick that you want to reset."
msgstr "Connecteu el llapis USB que voleu restablir."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   A new device appears in the list of storage devices. This new device\n"
"   corresponds to the USB stick that you plugged in. Click on it.\n"
msgstr ""
"   Apareix un nou dispositiu a la llista de dispositius d'emmagatzematge. "
"Aquest nou dispositiu\n"
"   correspon al llapis USB que heu connectat. Feu-hi clic.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"In the right pane of the window, verify that the device corresponds to the "
"USB stick that you want to reset, its brand, its size, etc."
msgstr ""
"Al panell dret de la finestra, comproveu que el dispositiu correspon al "
"llapis USB que voleu restablir, la seva marca, la seva mida, etc."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"To reset the USB stick, click on the <span class=\"guimenu\">[[!img lib/open-"
"menu.png alt=\"Menu\" class=symbolic link=no]]</span> button in the titlebar "
"and choose <span class=\"guilabel\">Format Disk…</span>."
msgstr ""
"Per restablir el llapis USB, feu clic al botó <span class=\"guimenu\">[[!img "
"lib/open-menu.png alt=\"Menú\" class=symbolic link=no]]</span> a la barra de "
"títol i trieu <span class=\"guilabel\">Formata disc...</span>."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "In the <span class=\"guilabel\">Format Disk</span> dialog:"
msgstr "Al diàleg <span class=\"guilabel\">Formata el disc</span>:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   1. If you want to erase all data securely, choose to\n"
"   **Overwrite existing data with zeroes** in the\n"
"   **Erase** menu.\n"
msgstr ""
"   1. Si voleu esborrar totes les dades de manera segura, trieu\n"
"   **Sobreescriu les dades existents amb zeros** al\n"
"   Menú **Esborra**.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   2. Choose **Compatible with all systems and devices (MBR/DOS)**\n"
"   in the **Partitioning** menu.\n"
msgstr ""
"   2. Trieu **Compatible amb tots els sistemes i dispositius (MBR/DOS)**\n"
"   al menú de **Particions**.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '   3. '
msgid "Click on the **Format…** button."
msgstr "Feu clic al botó **Formata...**."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"In the confirmation dialog, click on the <span class=\"bold\">Format</span> "
"button to confirm."
msgstr ""
"Al diàleg de confirmació, feu clic al botó <span class=\"bold\">Formata</"
"span> per confirmar."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"To make sure that all the changes are written to the USB stick, click on the "
"<span class=\"guimenu\">[[!img lib/media-eject.png alt=\"Eject\" "
"class=symbolic link=no]]</span> button in the titlebar."
msgstr ""
"Per assegurar-vos que tots els canvis s'escriuen al llapis USB, feu clic al "
"botó <span class=\"guimenu\">[[!img lib/media-eject.png alt=\"Extreu\" "
"class=symbolic link=no]]</span> de la barra de títol."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Resetting a Tails USB stick from itself"
msgstr "Restablir un llapis USB Tails des de si mateix"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If Tails is your only Linux system, you can generally reset a Tails USB "
"stick directly from that USB stick while running Tails."
msgstr ""
"Si Tails és el vostre únic sistema Linux, generalment podeu restablir un "
"llapis USB de Tails directament des d'aquest llapis USB mentre feu servir "
"Tails."

#. type: Bullet: '1.  '
msgid ""
"When starting Tails, add the <span class=\"command\">toram</span> boot "
"option in the <span class=\"application\">Boot Loader</span>. For detailed "
"instructions, see the documentation on [[using the <span class=\"application"
"\">Boot Loader</span>|advanced_topics/boot_options]]."
msgstr ""
"Quan inicieu Tails, afegiu l'opció d'arrencada <span class=\"command\""
">toram</span> al <span class=\"application\">Carregador d'Arrencada</span>. "
"Per obtenir instruccions detallades, consulteu la documentació sobre com [["
"usar el <span class=\"application\">Carregador d'Arrencada</span>|"
"advanced_topics/boot_options]]."

#. type: Bullet: '2.  '
msgid ""
"If Tails starts as usual, follow the instructions for [[resetting a USB "
"stick using <span class=\"application\">GNOME Disks</span>|linux#disks]]."
msgstr ""
"Si Tails s'inicia com de costum, seguiu les instruccions per [[restablir un "
"llapis USB mitjançant <span class=\"application\">Discs de "
"GNOME</span>|linux#disks]]."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    **If the system fails to start**, that means that the computer does not have\n"
"    enough memory for this operation mode. Try with another computer, or find\n"
"    another Linux system, such as another Tails USB stick, to do the reset from.\n"
msgstr ""
"    **Si el sistema no s'inicia**, vol dir que l'ordinador no té\n"
"    memòria suficient per a aquest mode de funcionament. Proveu amb un altre "
"ordinador o trobeu\n"
"    un altre sistema Linux, com un altre llapis USB de Tails, per fer el "
"restabliment.\n"

